Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:07.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You absolutely sure you can do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:08.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't have agreed to it if I couldn't. Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Speaking of cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:14.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,I got a little something I need to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:17.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like keeping an eye on a house full of critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:20.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,that was totally what I was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.28,Spike,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.28,0:00:25.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Go to your welcoming thing in the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:27.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Spike's got it all under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:37.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,we can't miss our train!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:38.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.29,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,This is going to be a real treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.78,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance said she'd never seen a crystal pony so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Of course they're excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:49.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They're up for the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:53.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's only the biggest sporting event in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Didn't Cloudsdale host the Equestria Games one year?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:56.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:59.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale should have hosted the games one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:02.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget when we got the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Equestria Games go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,the city of Fillydelphia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:15.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,NOOOOOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.70,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,These crystal ponies lost a thousand years to an evil king's curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:23.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,They've had enough bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:27.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No way we're letting them experience the pain of losing out on these games.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance is counting on us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:33.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to do our part to convince the games inspector to choose the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:36.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And we are not going to let her down. Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,NOOOOOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:42.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I was just answering Twilight's question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Four, three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.21,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ok, everypony, great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.55,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sounds like we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.24,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,One more time, from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.74,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, I think that was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:42.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, we've run this like twelve times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:43.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think we got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:47.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Cadence said the games inspector really puts focus to the ring on her visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's no margin for error here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And this means we must practice the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,On a train car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You heard the pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,On your hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Two, four, six, eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.02,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Crystal Empire, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Watch your step leaving the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Probably should have watched our step while we were still on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wow! The Crystal Empire looks crystaller then ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:30.95,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They must have every pony in the Empire out sprucing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This must be why we're asked to handle the welcome commitee routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:39.41,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it's probably also because we will be awesome at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.08,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,These ponies do look pretty darn excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yup, I remember that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:50.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But not as much as I remember the crushing wave of disappointment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,that came when things didn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:57.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That is the face I do not want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.53,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,There are my girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sunshine, sunshine, ladybugs awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:15.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Clap your hooves and do a little shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This is spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Please, everypony, stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:21.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I need air!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.92,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and try whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.12,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,It's all complimentary for the welcome commitee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.32,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,That over there is a crystal mud bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:32.40,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,which relaxes your body and rejuvenates your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:36.57,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Now I realize it can be kind of strange to climb into mud,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.98,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,but if you'll just give it a chance, I'm sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.00,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So relaxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie, honestly…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:55.99,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:59.61,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Have a good time while I have my ceremonial headdress done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ceremonial… headdress?..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:06.55,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,, When meeting with important guests, it was a tradition for rulers of the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:10.18,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,to weave crystals into their manes in a very specific way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:13.03,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,The games inspector is known for doing her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:17.25,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,, She'll certainly be expecting my look to reflect th importance of her visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.90,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,if I may have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I-I have two pieces of news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,First, your mane stylist has the flu and won't be able to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:29.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,for fear of you catching it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.88,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Well...I hope she's better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:37.97,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Do any of the other stylists here know how to do the traditional royal ceremonial headdress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.65,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Just a small detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're trying to land the Equestria Games here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as a small detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:56.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.18,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Oh Rarity, you would do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:00.95,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Way to step it up, Rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:05.04,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I have all the precise instructions right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.20,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,You sure you're up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:17.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Working on the hair of royalty on such an auspicious occasion is the opportunity of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I will give it everything I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:21.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See? No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:24.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Besides, the games inspector isn't expected for several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:28.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'll have plenty of time to figure out exactly how to… do… t his…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:31.31,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:33.79,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,You said you had a second bit of news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The games inspector, Miss Harshwhinny will be arriving on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What!? You couldn't have told us that news first!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's fifteen minutes from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.29,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How long before Cadance is ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm sure to find some shortcuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can you have her back at the castle when we're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Everypony, just look out for the pony with the flower print luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy, pudding-in-a-freezy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'll bring the Games Inspector back to the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,put on our big welcome committee how-do-you-do and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:16.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Put the pudding out before eating or you'll crack a tooth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll just ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We need to remember that the Games Inspector arriving early
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:25.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,is probably part of a plan to psyche us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself. She's got a rep for catching hosts off-guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:34.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,just to see if we can handle the kind of massive pressure that comes with hosting the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:36.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no... we're gonna blow it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:41.31,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not if we always stay one step ahead and don't fall for any of her mind games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Anything she throws at us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,we just needs to remember she's testing us, and roll with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:57.93,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.31,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.14,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I know you're not expecting us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but we're here to personally welcome you to the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.83,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,The whole lot of you came to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, um, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:21.17,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Well, darn tootin' ain't that the cat's meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:22.75,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Y'all didn't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.86,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Why, I hardly expected anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:29.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The Princess wouldn't have had it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.53,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,The Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.82,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,None other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:36.09,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Well, tie me up and throw me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:38.52,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,this just keeps gettin' better and better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Can we help you with your bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.63,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:44.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I love flower print!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:45.89,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:50.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Our first stop is the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:53.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,where we got a razzamatazzy welcome planned for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.74,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,The castle? Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.62,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Hot-diggety-dawg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See that? We just gotta roll with it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:04.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,until the Princess gets there and we'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.53,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,So, uh... how's it going so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.39,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It's just... oh so complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:26.81,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Fix what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I, I, was, looking for shortcuts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.53,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and I thought step twelve was optional!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.90,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.69,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,My golly, the crystal castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.31,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Well, I've seen pictures
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.70,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,but I never expected to see it with my very own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.75,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,From the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, she's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're letting her lull you into a false sense of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:02.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Watch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,it's all part of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.58,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.19,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Mind if I take a quick run outside first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:16.27,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,It was an awfully long train ride and my legs could use a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:19.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... we were just about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:23.10,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh, never you mind. You go on ahead. I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She was probably testing us to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,if we could remain in control of a complex situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Looks like we passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:38.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'd like to thank you for this opportunity to introduce you to this wonderful kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.51,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, the pleasure is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And since we're not even from here ourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:47.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,who better than us to let you know just how welcoming this place can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Two, four, six, eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Name a place that's really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Please? keep coming back for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Two, seven, nine, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The place that we all wanna be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Four, three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.37,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire, that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:13.09,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I tell ya, I have travelled far and wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:16.07,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but I have never, ever been welcomed any place
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,in a fashion that you all have done here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:23.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance would be so glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.90,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm surprised she knows anything about me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's been looking forward to your visit for weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.57,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh goodie! Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:39.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where the heck is she anyway? Wasn't she supposed to be here by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.46,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:47.18,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Maybe… I-I-I'll just take a little run outside now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Or, if you like, we could give you a tour of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:58.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That way, you could be learning and stretching all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.88,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oooh, tour of the Crystal Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.44,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I'd love that a whole heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Dash, we've hardly have even been here before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's just another test!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:10.78,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're gotta roll with it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:12.99,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I may give the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.89,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, I'll do it! I'll be, I'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:16.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You'll start giving her the tour, and I'll go see what's keeping Cadence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.58,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,Hello yourself. First hello of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We finished the welcome commitee song
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and we just wanted to introduce Miss Hearshwhinny to…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:46.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,No! No, Princess Cadance isn't ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Somethings gone terribly wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I need to speak to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You can't, You mustn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.20,Rarity,,0,0,0,,she's in the middle of the delicate conditioning rinse that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.65,Rarity,,0,0,0,,must go perfectly if it is to be any hope for her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on. How bad could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:01.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Imagine her mane turned into a porcupine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Please, I will bring her back from the brink of tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but you have got to buy me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There's no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:11.90,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So, you see this here? This, uhm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.93,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,this is, uhm…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A big round room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's known for its roundness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And bigness. And did I mention that it's round?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.37,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I think thay call it a rotunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.33,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,A small, confining rotunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Round is round, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Easy, Pinkie. Let's play the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:37.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We've got her in a good mood, so let's not do anything to ruin that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:40.92,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,You know, I love this sort of architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.48,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I detect a neogothic inspiration in the design. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And not a moment too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.76,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Where's Cadence? Please tell me she's right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:01.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's a bit of a problem with her headdress. How's it going here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.63,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I, uh, hate to be a bother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.90,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,but the legs are crumping up on me with all this standing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:14.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's getting bored. And we have to buy Rarity some more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll see if Shining Armor can come help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can't one of you other ponies take over in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.61,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wanna stretch your legs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:28.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever you need, I'm sure we can provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Let's just make our way to the castle's gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Our tour will now be headed…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And we're walking, and we're walking…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.48,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Twily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor, You've gotta help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.16,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've left the other ponies behind giving the Games Inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the worst castle tour ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.77,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Come on, gang! Are we gonna gallop, or are we gonna trot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:12.11,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Castle tour, huh? I'm pretty sure I can give you a hoof on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.57,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Let's move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.09,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Everything's gonna be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:18.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:22.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.62,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I'm outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.99,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Feels so good to stretch my old legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.33,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Turns out, Crystal Castle doesn't have a gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.22,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.07,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Make her... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:41.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's the games inspector! Let her do her thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:44.26,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Good! These hooves! I'm outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.99,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:51.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But that's why she's in charge of choosing who gets the games, and we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.38,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Take me outside for a run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.12,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, we need to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Where's she going in such a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.13,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I think we've got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.87,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Whoo! Why! Whoa! That felt good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.98,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a great run to shake the cobwebs off of those old bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.09,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Hey there, speedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:47.37,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Ah, these wide open spaces y'all got here remind me of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.14,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:53.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, so, you're enjoying your visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:56.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.30,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh, good golly, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.68,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I just love to travel and see new places.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.74,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful spot you got here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:07.38,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you so much! I'm Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.92,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,The prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:15.35,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it, just locking up the games for the Crystal Empire is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.77,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Ain't no thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:21.66,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,My oh my! I've never met a prince before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.07,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:26.89,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I think in your line of working you meet princes all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.07,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:31.81,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Just an ordinary wild mustang from Mustangia
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.28,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,here to enjoy a little vacay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.61,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Never thought that I'd also be meeting a royalty to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You are... Miss Harshwhinny,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,the Equestria Games inspector, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.44,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Inspector what, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:52.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We got the wrong pony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:55.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,NNNOOOOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.11,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,YEESSSSSSS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:08.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, please, still be here! Oh please oh please oh please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:12.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's got to be another pony with flower print luggage around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Except that there isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:18.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We've got to find her before Cadence finds out what a mess we've made of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:20.19,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We split the Empire up into five sectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Each of us searches a sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:27.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Except for the spa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What's the point of checking there? That's where Cadence is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,If Miss Harshwhinny is there, well, then game over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:38.26,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,Every city in the Empire wants to host the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.57,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,So, I have to go through all the big phoney baloney song and dance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.66,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,though of course I'm never getting the real inside scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:49.56,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh, golly I've been having a swell time since I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.07,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,I'm actually thinking of extending my stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:55.58,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,And what exactly has made your visit so "special"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:58.75,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh, where to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:06.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're in luck! I don't either of them knows yet that the other one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Wonderful news!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Look! Princess Cadence, better than new!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.11,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.52,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,So, this is where you've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:23.30,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,I will let you know, this is by far the worst welcome I had in all my years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.64,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! What was wrong with your welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.79,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,There wasn't one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:30.79,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:35.66,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,, Princess, we gave our welcome to the wrong pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.23,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Left the right one waiting at the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:40.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,and completely ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Cinnamon bun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,When I was a little filly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:51.52,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I wanted it so badly for Cloudsdale to win the Equestria Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.74,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but it didn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So I thought I could make up for that disappointment by helping
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,the Crystal Empire win the chance to host the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:02.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But it looks like I've ruined your chances instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.72,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, speedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.85,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,I just finished hearing about how this pony
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.81,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,was just treated to the warmest, funnest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.48,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,most fabulous reception she ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.63,FakeInspector,,0,0,0,,Darn tootin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:16.20,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,Courtesy of these fine ponies right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:19.27,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,Which, in my expert opinion, amounts to the first ever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:23.68,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,unvanished, unrehearsed and unbiased appraisal of a potential host
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.88,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,of the Equestria Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.16,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,which can only mean one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:31.83,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,The next host of the Equestria Games is…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.83,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:38.22,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, crystal ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:49.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You know, it feels good to help others get something you always wanted never had!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.20,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Almost as good as getting it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:57.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'll still be able to come back here and watch the games when they're played.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.05,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're right. That'll rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.88,0:21:04.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.91,Mrs.Harshwhinny,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Bummer Spike had to miss out on all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.29,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,He woulda' have fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's having a great time watching all the critters back at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Think he's still got a handle on things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If he's staying calm and collected,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I bet he's doing a terrific job as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You all hear that?
